et-firstboot - EmComm-Tools First Boot Wizard
Author: Sylvain Deguire (VA2OPS)
Date: January 2026

Flask-based web UI for initial system configuration.
Runs on first boot to collect user info and configure services.

Includes download support for:
- ET Map Tilesets (.mbtiles) from GitHub releases
- OSM Maps (.pbf) from Geofabrik for Navit navigation
- Wikipedia (.zim) from Kiwix for offline reference
